<font color="yellow"><i>Kau mau ke taman hiburan bersama kami?</i></font>

536
00:32:35,149 --> 00:32:36,649
<font color="yellow"><i>Lalu kau mau pergi dengan siapa?</i></font>

537
00:32:36,649 --> 00:32:38,979
<font color="yellow"><i>Borg Mom, kau tahu aku
selalu berada di pihakmu?</i></font>

538
00:32:38,979 --> 00:32:40,620
<font color="yellow"><i>Dasar dia. Lihatlah matanya.</i></font>

539
00:32:40,620 --> 00:32:42,249
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia tidak bisa
mengalihkan pandangan darinya.</i></font>

540
00:32:42,249 --> 00:32:43,519
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku akan menghancurkannya.</i></font>

541
00:32:43,519 --> 00:32:45,890
<font color="yellow"><i>Selamat datang di pondok Boo Ti Na!</i></font>

542
00:32:45,890 --> 00:32:46,890
<font color="yellow"><i>Kalian sudah datang.</i></font>

543
00:32:46,890 --> 00:32:48,789
<font color="yellow"><i>Keluar. Sekarang!</i></font>

544
00:32:48,789 --> 00:32:50,629
<font color="yellow"><i>Tunggu, aku memintanya untuk datang.</i></font>

545
00:32:50,629 --> 00:32:51,629
<font color="yellow"><i>Do Hye.</i></font>

546
00:32:51,629 --> 00:32:54,370
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia terus melanggar peraturan.</i></font>

547
00:32:54,370 --> 00:32:55,399
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau masih di sini?</i></font>

548
00:32:55,399 --> 00:32:57,970
<font color="yellow"><i>Kudengar semua orang tua
dan guru pada kesana.</i></font>

549
00:32:57,970 --> 00:32:59,499
<font color="yellow"><i>Omo, dia di sini.</i></font>

550
00:32:59,499 --> 00:33:02,109
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa dia
selalu membuat Borg Mom kesulitan?</i></font>

551
00:33:02,109 --> 00:33:04,810
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa dia terus
melayang-layang di sekitar Borg Mom?</i></font>

